{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782388847241,"sessionID":"ses_1015ca6cfffeteaDphZUZFsMdV","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"apply_patch","callID":"call_WFdBKE6C7Lg6T1WxCNpitOXO","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"patchText":"*** Begin Patch\n*** Add File: D:\\Users\\Sieger\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\opencode\\phase03-matrix-patch.json\n+{\n+  \"updates\": [\n+    {\n+      \"featureId\": \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-login-1ed35246b3-002-navigation-surface-menu-drawer-toolbar-o\",\n+      \"set\": {\n+        \"verificationEvidence\": [\n+          \"Source review: D:/Kotlin2Cangjie/Foodike/app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/login/LoginScreen.kt calls `navController.navigate(Screen.Home.route)` from `PerformLogin` and uses `popUpTo(navController.graph.findStartDestination().id) { inclusive = true }` to clear the prior flow.\",\n+          \"Target review: entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.performLogin calls `navigateTo(loginStore.successRoute())` only after credential validation succeeds, and entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/features/login/login_store.cj::successRoute returns the home route contract.\",\n+          \"Focused test harness blocker: 2026-06-25 bounded reproduction of `C:/Users/Sieger/.cangjie-sdk/6.1/cangjie/build-tools/tools/bin/cjpm.exe test --target aarch64-linux-ohos` from `D:/workspace/Foodike/Foodike-Harmony/entry/src/test/cangjie` progressed past the earlier `profile.build.combined` configuration error after updating `entry/src/test/cangjie/cjpm.toml`, but link failed with missing `Scrt1.o`, `crti.o`, `crtn.o`, `-lm`, and `-lc`; see translation-inputs/test-build-reports/phase-03-onboarding-login-profile/test-build-report.md plus 2026-06-25 manual reproduction output.\"\n+        ]\n+      }\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"featureId\": \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-login-34c5f4ba3a-006-settings-preferences-option-toggles-or-c\",\n+      \"set\": {\n+        \"verificationEvidence\": [\n+          \"Source review: D:/Kotlin2Cangjie/Foodike/app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/login/LoginViewModel.kt validates credentials and then calls `repository.toggleLoginState()` before invoking the success navigation callback.\",\n+          \"Target review: entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/features/login/login_store.cj::LoginStore.login persists login state through LoginPreferencesService when credentials match.\",\n+          \"Target review: entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/data/session/login_preferences_service.cj::LoginPreferencesService.login writes `user_login_state=true` into HarmonyOS Preferences and flushes it immediately.\",\n+          \"Focused test harness blocker: translation-inputs/test-build-reports/phase-03-onboarding-login-profile/test-build-report.md records TEST_COMPILE_FAIL, and the 2026-06-25 bounded reproduction after fixing `entry/src/test/cangjie/cjpm.toml` shows SDK/linker missing `Scrt1.o`, `crti.o`, `crtn.o`, `-lm`, and `-lc`, so test files are present but cannot be counted as PASS evidence in this environment.\"\n+        ]\n+      }\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"featureId\": \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-login-78d5c742f4-007-observable-state-viewmodel-flow-livedata\",\n+      \"set\": {\n+        \"verificationEvidence\": [\n+          \"Source review: D:/Kotlin2Cangjie/Foodike/app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/login/LoginScreen.kt reads `val email by viewModel.email`, `val password by viewModel.password`, and collects `eventFlow` inside `LaunchedEffect` to show snackbar feedback.\",\n+          \"Target review: entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj declares `@State` loginEmail, loginPassword, and loginErrorMessage, updates them from `renderLoginRoute`, and reuses them in `performLogin` and `clearLoginError`.\",\n+          \"Target review: entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos