fordances, while entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.buildProfileRoute and performLogout bind those actions to runtime route transitions.\",\n1045:         \"Target review: entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/features/profile/profile_store.cj::ProfileStore.backRoute and logoutRoute preserve the source-consistent history/onboarding destinations used by bootstrap_page.cj.\",\n1046:         \"Build verification: translation-inputs/build-reports/phase-03-onboarding-login-profile/build-report.md recorded PASS for the phase-03 onboarding/login/profile implementation.\",\n1047:         \"Focused test harness blocker: translation-inputs/test-build-reports/phase-03-onboarding-login-profile/test-build-report.md records TEST_COMPILE_FAIL; 2026-06-25 bounded reproduction after fixing `entry/src/test/cangjie/cjpm.toml` reaches SDK/linker failure for missing `Scrt1.o`, `crti.o`, `crtn.o`, `-lm`, and `-lc`.\"\n1048:       ],\n1049:       \"parityLevel\": \"equivalent\",\n1050:       \"targetEndpoints\": [\n1051:         \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/features/profile/profile_page.cj::buildProfileTopBar\",\n1052:         \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/features/profile/profile_page.cj::renderProfileRoute\",\n1053:         \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.buildProfileRoute\",\n1054:         \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.performLogout\",\n1055:         \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/features/profile/profile_store.cj::ProfileStore.backRoute\",\n1056:         \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/features/profile/profile_store.cj::ProfileStore.logoutRoute\",\n1057:         \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/app_router.cj::routePath\"\n1058:       ],\n1059:       \"tests\": [],\n1060:       \"notes\": \"The target uses a single route-host st